<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2017</DATELINE><TITLE>Hyper Acute Demyelinating Encephalomyelitis of Childhood: A Rare Entity</TITLE><BODY>A young child with catastrophic neurological illness diagnosed as a rare variant of acute demyelinating encephalomyelitis (ADEM). She succumbed to her illness despite of aggressive and appropriate management. Malignant demyelinating encephalomyelitis should be considered in children who are refractory to the treatment of ADEM.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>